<p>Chris talks about an image work-flow using folders, he answers questions about ND filters and flash diffusers and he discusses the 2011 Himalayan Trek with Jon Miller, host of <a href="http://therestofeverest.com/">The Rest of Everest</a>.</p>
<p>You will also find out about Chris&#8217; journey into the realm of large format photography.</p>
